  <summary date="2019-08-29T21:51:56Z" status="Introduced in House">Clean Slate Act of 2018

This bill requires courts to automatically seal records for certain arrests and nonviolent offenses involving marijuana. Additionally, the bill creates a mechanism to allow an individual to petition to seal criminal records for certain other nonviolent offenses.</summary>
